::Iron Raptor::

IR shakes her head, remembering Plintissa. But there wasn't any time for flashbacks right now. She needed to get on with the training.

"No, she's not here. She left a while ago," she replies, walking quickly through Maximal City toward the training rooms.



--- In nbwrpg@y..., "Soulstice Omega" <thecode@p...> wrote:
> Doom Ice and Rizopas waited for Stronghold and Blender to walk up, then the
> 4 follow Iron Raptor.
> 
> Doom Ice: You were once friends with Plintissa. I know because all she would
> do is whine about you, and how you had betrayed her, and how you didn't like
> her anymore.
> 
> Stronghold: Before you even met her, all she did was whine and cry.
> 
> Blender: And to think she was a veteran in the war.
> 
> Rizopas: She isn't here, right?...
